function SecondSectionComponent() { return (

CALL FOR PAPERS

Submission OPEN for the 2025 Edition

Deadline:
31st December, 2024, 11:59 PM (UTC+3:00)

Authors are cordially invited to submit papers to the upcoming Edition. The article can be submitted via the submitting form found below. If you face problems with paper submission, please feel free to contact the IYNA October Publication Team. Rules and Criteria for papers and articles are found below under the Rules & Criteria Section. Papers submitted to this journal will be deemed as they have not been published and are not under consideration for publication elsewhere.

); } export default SecondSectionComponent;
